UID:e2f2c39719c94b570e1196bed12d36de
SUMMARY:Digitale Leute Summit 2026
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261117
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20261118
LOCATION:Cologne, Germany
DESCRIPTION:Quelle: https://digitale-leute.de/summit/\nGermany’s leading cross-functional professional education and networking event focused on software product development, including UX/Design. The summit targets UX-Designers, Product- and Digital Managers, and Software Engineers. Day 1 (November 17) is the AI Deep Dive Day at Smartvillage Cologne, focusing on the practical application of AI across product, design, and engineering. Day 2 (November 18) is the Conference Day at Palladium Cologne, featuring talks, interviews, panels, and masterclasses for Product, Engineering, and UX Design professionals to learn how to develop better digital products.
END:VEVENT
