SUMMARY:Gamification in Fintech: From Boosting Engagement to Becoming a Lovemark
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260128
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260128
LOCATION:Online
DESCRIPTION:Quelle: https://www.interaction-design.org/literature/article/ux-conferences-calendar?srsltid=AfmBOoo7C52rsF4XF7bJf9V98RwciZt2UUcVgVzIdHmi-fQWPg5wZaUE\nCraft Innovations holds a session to explore how gamification impacts product goals, like retention, feature adoption, transaction frequency, loyalty, and more. Ideal for Product Managers in fintech and banking; UX / CX designers working on complex products; founders building consumer or B2B fintech solutions; innovation, growth, and digital teams.
