BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:1070a16a25c2a1b7585825859407a12c
SUMMARY:The prompt:UX Conference focuses on the intersection of artificial intelligence and user experience design, gathering designers, researchers, and product managers to explore how AI is reshaping UX.
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260121
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260122
LOCATION:Berlin, Germany
DESCRIPTION:Quelle: https://condens.io/guides/ux-conference-guide-2026/\nThe prompt:UX Conference focuses on the intersection of artificial intelligence and user experience design, gathering designers, researchers, and product managers to explore how AI is reshaping UX and how to prepare strategies, tools, and workflows accordingly. Expect engaging keynotes from industry leaders, hands-on workshops, case studies, and a dedicated networking reception, all aimed at helping your team integrate AI into UX in meaningful, future-ready ways. If you’re looking to stay at the forefront of AI-powered UX design and research, this conference offers the insights, practical learning, and connections to make that happen.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:acb6b7893fea51a0710259843c22b9e3
SUMMARY:DDX Tokyo brings together leaders in digital innovation, UX, design, product, and customer research. The theme "Innovation Meets Impact" emphasizes how user experience, AI, and strategic design converge to deliver measurable business outcomes.
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260204
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260204
LOCATION:Tokyo, Japan
DESCRIPTION:Quelle: https://condens.io/guides/ux-conference-guide-2026/\nDDX Tokyo brings together leaders in digital innovation, UX, design, product, and customer research. The theme "Innovation Meets Impact" emphasizes how user experience, AI, and strategic design converge to deliver measurable business outcomes. Expect a one-day programme of keynotes, panels, round-tables, and networking in a dynamic global setting.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:7626c3184f91eeccd3fa5266fc02ca30
SUMMARY:The UX360 Virtual Summit is a global online event for UX researchers and designers from around the world. It covers the full research journey — from planning and conducting studies to turning insights into actionable business outcomes.
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260204
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260205
LOCATION:Online
DESCRIPTION:Quelle: https://condens.io/guides/ux-conference-guide-2026/\nThe UX360 Virtual Summit is a global online event for UX researchers and designers from around the world. It covers the full research journey — from planning and conducting studies to turning insights into actionable business outcomes. Expect impactful keynotes, real-world case studies, interactive panels, round-tables, and high-value networking sessions — all delivered virtually. This is the must-attend virtual summit for UX research practitioners looking to level up their insight practice, connect globally, and drive measurable impact.
END:VEVENT
