DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260204
LOCATION:Tokyo, Japan
DESCRIPTION:Quelle: https://condens.io/guides/ux-conference-guide-2026/\nDDX Tokyo brings together leaders in digital innovation, UX, design, product, and customer research. The theme "Innovation Meets Impact" emphasizes how user experience, AI, and strategic design converge to deliver measurable business outcomes. Expect a one-day programme of keynotes, panels, round-tables, and networking in a dynamic global setting.
END:VEVENT
