SUMMARY:PUSH UX conference 2026
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261022
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20261023
LOCATION:Munich, Germany
DESCRIPTION:Quelle: https://push-conference.com/\nEurope’s largest international UX & Product Design event for experienced professionals, going strong since 2012. The conference takes place live in Munich, in the heart of Europe. It explores topics such as Product Design & UX Practice, Experience Economics, Shifting Careers, Practical AI, Design Impact, and Trends & Innovation. Attendees can connect with experienced Product Designers, UX Professionals, Researchers, User Minded Product Managers, and Creative Developers, from expert ICs to seasoned Leaders.
END:VEVENT
